rComments: Best prof ever. I love you professor McLeman. Amazing person
C'est sans aucun doute un des meilleurs profs du département de géographie de l'Université d'Ottawa!

Best prof I've had. Hands down. Truly cares for his students and you can see his passion for teaching. Makes the classes very interesting. Even if you're not into Env. Studies or Geography, this class could be an awesome elective. This class changed me in many ways and tought me a lot! Great music before class too :)

Such an amazing professor! I had no interest in taking this course and he made it one of my favourites. Quite funny and engaging. Lectures reflected exams identically. Loaded lectures slides online, made studying easy. Adorable and fun, makes lectures interesting.

This prof is awesome! I would completely recommend taking one of his classes! He is very understanding, easy to relate with and to get along with! He makes class fun, inspires thought provoking discussion and is just a wonderful professor! Outstanding to say the least!

Excellent prof. I would recommend him to anyone. He truly cares and makes class fun to go to. Tests were completely reflective of what we learned in class. I didn't really open my textbook at all and ended up with a B+. Great class
Great Prof! This man truly cares about his students and teaching. Very knowledgeable and helpful. I dont entirely like science so I was lost from time to time but the assgined textbook is great.
Awesome!  He is very funny and can anyone interested in the environment and wanting to help out!!  Great music at the begining of class :)

Always found new ways to interest students, related a lot of class content to his personal life, all of which helped keep me engaged and paying attention. I ended up with a B+ and went to about 75% of classes... the textbook was helpful! Id definitely take another of his classes :)

Robert is beyond amazing. I will take a class with him even if I am not interested in the class, simply because he is such a great prof! He is very passionate about what he teaches, teaches well, and really wants his students to succeed. Definitely an A+ prof. This guys should get an award or something.

BY FAR the best professor I have had so far. He makes the subject so interesting and finds creative ways to keep the class involved. The midterm, essay and final were all very fair. If you know your material and the main theories he taught, you will have no problem getting a fantastic grade and amazing knowledge about the environment. A+++++ Prof

Amazing professor, absolutely amazing. My high marks are warranted, amazing prof. His slides are always on VC before the class, theories and ideas are very coherent. Very strong lecture skills. Recommendation: Buy an older edition of the textbook on Amazon. Textbook costs 110 new, or $8 for an older edition on Amazon.

Great prof. Very nice man. He knows his material, and he explains things well. He can keep me interested in his subject matter SO well (given the fact that I had no interest in the course before I took it) that I dare say he is magic. Highly recommended.
AWESOME. Clear, funny and interesting. He has lived and experienced most of what he teaches. Could not ask fro anything better.
Great prof, great class.  He posts all of the lecture slides online so its easy to follow along.  His lectures are always very interesting.
Great prof, great class. Deffinitely my favourite class this year.
